org.identityconnectors.framework.api

Interface ConnectorInfoManager

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    LocalConnectorInfoManagerImpl, OsgiConnectorInfoManagerImpl, RemoteConnectorInfoManagerImpl

    public interface ConnectorInfoManager
    Maintains a list of ConnectorInfo instances, each of which describes a connector that is available.
    See Also:
    ConnectorInfoManagerFactory
